snippet.title: Luma Island release date announced!
snippet.description:
Feel Free Games is excited to announce that Luma Island, its upcoming co-op adventure set on a mysterious yet idyllic island, launches on November 20.

Explore a strange island, build your dream homestead, and master various professions in Luma Island on PC via Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2408820/Luma_Island

The game will also be available for its first public demo on October 14 as part of Steam Next Fest. 

__________________________

Stay up to date by following Luma Island on X, TikTok,  Facebook, YouTube, and Reddit as well as joining the official Luma Island Discord server to keep up with the latest news.

Discord: https://discord.gg/kd8TU4AVV2
X / Twitter: https://twitter.com/LumaIsland
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@lumaisland
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lumaisland
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@lumaisland
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/lumaisland/
Website: https://www.lumaisland.com
